 Storage requirement for 1.36B docs is ~434 GB, so at least 3 partitions are needed (480 GB total).  For production, 6 SUs (2 replicas × 3 partitions) is recommended for high availability and throughput. Keep 10–20% headroom for index overhead and rebuild operations.  Our 1.36B docs (~434 GB) fit in 3 partitions on S1. That’s 3 SUs minimum (~$736/mo) or 6 SUs (~$1,472/mo) for HA. Because headroom is only ~10%.									
									
									
									
									
